        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "After calling a dispatch() in a test, the resetResponse() method cleans the response object and the registry instance. However, the request object still contains param from the previous dispatch and so it contaminates the new one. I personally call $this->setUp() after every dispatch\/assertions cycle to ensure cleanliness.\nNot sure if it is the intended behaviour, I think reset the request object or provide a parameter of resetResponse() or a resetRequest() method would be useful."
        },
